{"tid":831341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務卿：維吾爾人在中國再教育營遭受可怕虐待","createTime":"2018-09-22T01:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T12:20:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddc6acf4bb3f756a6d7f95563c56bf3b07df336","tid":831341,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:03:40.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）今天痛批，被拘留在中國再教育營內的維吾爾族穆斯林遭到「可怕虐待」。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧以全球宗教自由現況為題發表演說時表示：「數以十萬計、甚至可能數以百萬計的維吾爾族人，遭強制拘留在所謂的再教育營內，被迫忍受嚴苛的政治教化和其他可怕虐待。」<br />\n<br />\n美國共和、民主兩黨國會議員8月下旬致函蓬佩奧和財長梅努欽（Steve Mnuchin），要求制裁涉及拘留維吾爾人的中國官員。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在演說中，並未提及是否會對中國官員採取懲罰措施。<br />\n<br />\n不過他在演說中也對中國基督教徒的命運深表憂慮。他說，中國的基督教徒已成為政府的鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3381533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F3381533&d=btRH%2BgKU%2F93JxdNHxl2m7P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e2ae96af\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3381533</a>"},{"pid":"279c202b14d7c5e0abdb0d2bcfda9f2110fa35c3","tid":831341,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔：今次就撐中國喇"},{"pid":"ef55fcd712a27e8fb216a423db1ed0352ef4d599","tid":831341,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:07:54.000Z","msg":"琴日制裁完裝備部長<br />\n今日準備制裁新疆官員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ff4a4f4516fb6a7ad026595fb52bac8407707d","tid":831341,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08b22bb746cfc56fa4f9ea43e69381d48a63211","tid":831341,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ff4a4f4516fb6a7ad026595fb52bac8407707d","tid":831341,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc